OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FThousands of rugby league fans from
OL,7,Facross Yorkshire will descend on Las
OL,8,FVegas this week ahead of a historic
OL,9,FSuper League match between champions
OL,10,FHull Kingston Rovers and the Leeds
OL,11,FRhinos.
OL,13,FThe game will take place at the 65,000-
OL,14,Fcapacity Allegiant Stadium on
OL,15,FSaturday, normally home to NFL side
OL,16,FLas Vegas Raiders, and will be
OL,17,Fbroadcast on British television,
OL,18,Falbeit with a midnight kick-off.
OL,20,FPoints will count towards the sides'
OL,21,Fdomestic campaigns.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
