PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FBut why is Super League going to Vegas?
OL,8,FThe fixture is the second time a Super
OL,9,FLeague match has been played in the
OL,10,FUnited States, after Wigan Warriors
OL,11,Ffaced Warrington Wolves last year.
OL,13,FAustralia's NRL had already taken
OL,14,Frugby league to the US the previous
OL,15,Fyear, as part of attempts to grow the
OL,16,Fgame and tap into the huge American
OL,17,Fmarket.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FAs well as Hull versus Leeds, this
OL,7,Fyear's bill includes two NRL contests,
OL,8,Fas Newcastle Knights play North
OL,9,FQueensland Cowboys and Canterbury
OL,10,FBulldogs take on St George-Illawarra
OL,11,FDragons.
OL,13,FWhether the sport can take a foothold
OL,14,Fin an already crowded sporting
OL,15,Fmarketplace remains to be seen.
OL,17,FBut for the fans flying out to Sin
OL,18,FCity, the prospect of watching their
OL,19,Fteams in a town more used to roulette
OL,20,Fthan rugby league is thrill enough.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
