OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,F'A once in a lifetime opportunity'
OL,8,FAmongst them are Rhinos supporters
OL,9,FJordan Baldwin and Adele Standring,
OL,10,Ffrom Halifax, who are making it a trip
OL,11,Fto remember by getting married on the
OL,12,FMonday after the match at the Little
OL,13,FWhite Wedding Chapel.
OL,15,F"I went to Vegas in 2018 with my mum,"
OL,16,Fsays Adele. "I saw a girl in a little
OL,17,Fwhite dress walk in front of the
OL,18,FBellagio fountains, and I thought
OL,19,F'that's going to be me!'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,F"When Wigan played Warrington (in
OL,7,FVegas) last year, I sprung the idea,"
OL,8,Fsays Jordan. "If the Rhinos get to
OL,9,FVegas, let's get married. I actually
OL,10,Fbought tickets to the match before I
OL,11,Fbought the engagement ring!"
OL,13,FThe couple will be joined by 15
OL,14,Ffriends and family for the big day.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, in the week leading up to
OL,17,Fgame day, fans will get the
OL,18,Fopportunity to explore Las Vegas'
OL,19,Ffamous casinos and unique ambience, as
OL,20,Fwell as meet some of their heroes and
OL,21,Fclub legends.
OL,26,@nD@_pmoD@Fpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
