PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FBoth the Leeds Rhinos and Hull KR have
OL,7,Fhired bars on The Strip, and will
OL,8,Fstage fan events and meet-and-greets
OL,9,Fwith club legends like Jamie Jones-
OL,10,FBuchanan, Danny McGuire and Barry
OL,11,FMcDermott.
OL,13,FThere will also be a chance for fans
OL,14,Fto meet members of the current teams
OL,15,Fat a signing session at the Resorts
OL,16,FWorld Hotel and a fan fest event at
OL,17,Fthe iconic Freemont Street Experience.
OL,19,FThis won't be the first time the
OL,20,FRhinos have played in the United
OL,21,FStates.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
