PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FIn 2008 they played an exhibition
OL,7,Fmatch against NRL team South Sydney
OL,8,FRabbitohs - co-owned by Hollywood
OL,9,Fsuperstar Russell Crowe - in
OL,10,FJacksonville, Florida. They returned
OL,11,Fin 2009 for a rematch with the
OL,12,FRabbitohs and again in 2016 for a pre-
OL,13,Fseason warm-weather training camp.
OL,15,F"It's a once in a lifetime
OL,16,Fopportunity," says Rhinos captain Ash
OL,17,FHandley. "I think everyone's buzzing
OL,18,Fto be out there. Go and enjoy it first
OL,19,Fof all, but we've got a job to do.
OL,20,FIt's going to have a Grand Final feel
OL,21,Fto it in round three."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
