PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FAlso making the trip are around 80
OL,7,Fyoung dancers from across Yorkshire,
OL,8,Fwho've been selected by Northern based
OL,9,Fcompany LeapX to perform on the pitch
OL,10,Fahead of the match. They'll join over
OL,11,F500 others from the USA and Australia.
OL,13,FThey have been practising for weeks,
OL,14,Fperfecting the special routine with
OL,15,Fthe help of leading NFL cheer
OL,16,Fchoreographers and performers.
OL,18,FMembers of the Leeds Rhinos cheer
OL,19,Fsquad, the Rhinestones, will make up
OL,20,Fpart of the travelling party.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,F"This is such an exciting opportunity
OL,7,Ffor young dancers," says Nicola Booth,
OL,8,Fdance development officer at the Leeds
OL,9,FRhinos Foundation.
OL,11,F"To be able to perform on one of the
OL,12,Fbiggest stages at a huge sporting
OL,13,Foccasion will be something they will
OL,14,Fnever forget. I am delighted that
OL,15,Fmembers of our own Rhinestones Dance
OL,16,FAcademy will be part of this once in a
OL,17,Flifetime experience."
OL,26,@yD@UO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
