CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FFrom East Yorkshire, Skirlaugh Amateur
OL,7,FRugby League Club is one of two UK
OL,8,Fteams flying out to Vegas to play in a
OL,9,Fnine-aside tournament against teams
OL,10,Ffrom all over the world.
OL,12,FThe club raised #30,000 to fund the
OL,13,Ftrip.
OL,15,FPlayer Joshua Atkinson said: "We've
OL,16,Fhad a tough, tough two years - bad
OL,17,Fresults, probably not where we wanted
OL,18,Fto be in the league table, so to get
OL,19,Fthis opportunity at the start of the
OL,20,Fyear... it's outstanding for the team
OL,21,Fand for the club as a whole."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FFellow squad member Lloyd Gurnell
OL,7,Fadded: "These things don't happen too
OL,8,Foften and we thought maybe it was
OL,9,Fbiting off more than we could chew,
OL,10,Fbut through the support of everyone
OL,11,Fand through will and and our own hard
OL,12,Fwork as a group, to get 30 odd of us
OL,13,Fto go across to the other side of the
OL,14,Fworld, it's, it's no small feat."
OL,16,FHe said the players would make the
OL,17,Fmost of tourist opportunities while in
OL,18,FVegas.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
