CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772044828
OL,3,CWhy is rugby's Super League being
OL,4,Cplayed in Las Vegas?
OL,6,FCoach Matthew Danville said the club
OL,7,Fwouldn't be treating it as a holiday
OL,8,Fthough.
OL,10,F"We are using it as a bit of a
OL,11,Ftraining camp," he said. "We're taking
OL,12,F35 players including staff out there,
OL,13,Fso we're not going out there for a
OL,14,Fholiday."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
